item.title: How do i make a new port for my rsps and make it not freeze when i atk something
item.dc:creator: @jamessemple jamessemple
item.description:
@jamessemple wrote:

lol go to server.java and search ur current port and keep changing to the port u want.
then go to client.java in ur client and search the port number u currently have and change those.
and then go to gui and check for any current port numbers in there and change those
last of all u need to change the port settings for ur utorrent/router and ur done
